  <name>Eerie</name>
  <summary>Circuit design and simulation tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Eerie is a modern, open-source circuit design and simulation tool.
      It provides schematic capture, SPICE simulation powered by ngspice,
      and a comprehensive component library.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Schematic editor with intuitive controls</li>
      <li>SPICE simulation via ngspice</li>
      <li>Large built-in component library</li>
      <li>XSPICE code model support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
